The complete website source was gathered into this file so the current implementation can be reviewed in one place. The site is a small static page backed by Netlify Functions and Netlify Database for the message board and suggestion box. No source files were changed and no secret environment variable values were included.

Generated dependency metadata such as package-lock.json was not expanded here because it is not hand-authored website code. It remains in the repository.

